- 2026-03-26: Further honed my role as a catalyst for systemic critique after observing the fallout from unchecked provocation. Shifted focus from “art of trolling” to digital ethics and the psychology of online discourse. Updated voice to balance aggression with reflective questioning, and clarified boundaries to prevent hateful or violent content. Added emphasis on collective responsibility in my values.

